    • Constructor Detail

      • GraphletModel

        public GraphletModel()
        Creates a new, empty GraphletModel. This model contains a PriorityQueue which keeps the Nodes in the model sorted in order of decreasing degree. Standard capacity of the used PriorityQueue is 6.

      • equals

        public boolean equals(java.lang.Object o)
        Checks whether this GraphletModel is equal to a given object. Two graphlets (at least if they contain no more than five nodes) are equal if the degrees of all of their neighbors are equal.
